00037 void GeometricNode::accept(INodeVisitor* visitor) {
00038         visitor->visit(this);
00039         if (visitor->getDirection() == INodeVisitor::upwards) {
00040                 for(unsigned i = 0; i < getNumberOfParents(); ++i) // recursively go up the graph structure
00041                 {
00042                         getParent(i)->accept(visitor);
00043                 }
00044         }
00045 }
